@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_oaegby(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = (wp.abs((v1 + 0.25 / v1 + 0.36)) / wp.cos(v0))
    tmp = wp.cos(wp.cos(v2))
    v2 = wp.exp(wp.exp(wp.sin(v1 + 0.88)))
    tmp = wp.sin((0.65 / (v0 + 0.62 + v1 + 0.72)))
    v1 = wp.exp(wp.abs((tmp + 0.85 - tmp + 0.32)))
    data[tid] = v0
